{"id": "1456257856339709983", "channel_id": "1456257856339709983", "type": 0, "author_id": "330867601691639809", "author_name": "rain_scarlet", "author_bot": false, "content": "Rey-Khan\n\nRealm: Caro\nType: Warden\nBirthday: 17th Nov\nGender: Female\nNous index: 31\nBased on: Aiueb Gnshal\n\n\n“ You have forgotten me, brother. But these eyes, they do not forget. ”\n\n【Memory】, 【Character】, and 【Emotion】—\nThe strange and fragile coordinates by which a self is drawn.\nTo most beings, they are no more than a passing mirage: impressions that erode, dissolve, and are ultimately forgotten. Yet there are those who linger too long at the edge of the unknown. Those who stare into the void until it begins, inevitably, to stare back.\nFor the void does not merely observe. It remembers.\nThe uninvited horrors beyond the stars, ancient and unbound by time, fixed their gaze upon her when all others had forgotten. From their remembrance, they fashioned a new her—not reborn, but reconstructed. Not restored, but defined.\nThus, she exists only as what they recall her to be.\nShe cannot change. She cannot escape.\nFor to be remembered is not salvation, nor annihilation—\nIt is entrapment.\nA perfect, eternal confinement,\nsealed within a prison known as “yourself.”\n\n(Art by chatGPT, i cant fking draw）", "timestamp": "2026-01-01T12:08:48.914000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-01T12:11:13.513000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [{"id": "1456257856708935845", "filename": "ChatGPT_Image_Jan_1_2026_08_08_41_PM.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2198730, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1456257856339709983/1456257856708935845/ChatGPT_Image_Jan_1_2026_08_08_41_PM.png?ex=69cbb951&is=69ca67d1&hm=c1f98cbfdabb616dab09e83712239483576c900aa6563d08b7ed82ea9e820554&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1456257856339709983", "flags": 0, "thread_title": 