{"id": "1456258062603255981", "channel_id": "1456257856339709983", "type": 0, "author_id": "330867601691639809", "author_name": "rain_scarlet", "author_bot": false, "content": "Stats: \nCon: 150\nAtk: 120\nDef: 138\nNo Psyche Surge: 【33.6% Death Resistance】 【10% Crit Rate】\nPsyche Surge +12: 【100.8% Death Resistance】【29.2% Crit Rate】\n\nTalent:\n【The Seventh Eye】: Whenever an ally deals damage to an enemy, if the enemy did not die, put a【Revel of the Void】into your hand. This effect can only trigger twice per turn.\n\n【Revel of the Void】（0 Cost)【Retain】：Lose 10% of your current health and gain an equal amount of blood furnace. Gain shield equal to 40% of Rey-Khan’s Def. Gain 1 stack of 【Oblivion】. 【Oblivion】carry forward to the next battle. You can only have at most 10 stacks of 【Oblivion】 at a time.\n\n【Soulforge Aplitude】: Rey-Khan‘s shielding can trigger critical shielding, and shielding is increased by 20~50% on crit. All Awakener’s “Defence” base shield amount is increased by 15~35%.\n\nSkills\n\nExalt \n【Gaze from the void】: [Devour: Your shielding and healing this turn is increased by 15%, put 1 additional copy of 【Revel of the Void】into your hand] \nGain shield equal to 90% of Rey-khan’s Def. Put 1 copy of 【Revel of the Void】into your hand. At the end of this turn, if you have at least 7 stacks of 【Oblivion】，consume all 【Oblivion】and deal 3% current health damage to the enemy with the highest health equals for each stack of 【Oblivion】\n\nOver-Exalt\n【Court of the Slumbering One】: Increase your handsize this turn by 2, put 2 more copies of 【Revel of the Void】into your hand, % current health damage from 【Oblivion】is increased to 4% per stack.", "timestamp": "2026-01-01T12:09:38.091000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-02T01:58:01.036000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1456257856339709983", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Doorstain's dissoluted siste Rey-Khan OC kit (Meme sorta)", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359914895646811", "1182359790249332756"]}
{"id": "1456258103270969397", "channel_id": "1456257856339709983", "type": 0, "author_id": "330867601691639809", "author_name": "rain_scarlet", "author_bot": false, "content": "Rouse\n【Eternal Confinement】（2 cost): Rey-Khan gains 50 aliemus. Rouse: 【Revel of the Void】in addition also deals damage to all enemies equals to 40% of Rey-Khan‘s Atk and increases Embryo fusion by 20%.\n\n【Shattered Flesh】(1 cost）: Gain Shield equal to 15% of Rey-Khan’s Def and blood furnace equal to 10% of your max health. Inflict weakness to all enemies for 1 turn. This card is treated as “Defence”\n\n【Broken Mind】（5 cost): 【Retain】: Whenever a【Revel of the Void】is played, reduce the cost of this card by 1 before use. Gain 20 aliemus. Deal damage equal to 500% of Rey-Khan’s Atk to the enemy with the highest health. Gain Alert equal to 7% of Rey-Khan’s Def, put a 【Revel of the Void】into your hand.\n\n【Strike】(1 cost): Deal damage equal to 20% of Rey-Khan’s Atk. Rey-Khan gain 10 aliemus.\n\n【Defence】(1 cost): Gain shield equal to 20% of Rey-Khan’s Def. Rey-Khan gain 10 aliemus.\n\n\nEnlighten:\n\nE1【Fragment of past self】: For every 1% Crit rate Rey-Khan and her equipped WoD & Covenant have，her shielding and aliemus gain is increased by 0.5%. After each DR proc, Rey-Khan gain blood furnace up to the furnace capacity.\n\nE2【Formless Black Void】: Increase the final damage of 【Broken Mind】by 5% for each 【Revel of the Void】played during this battle. \n\nE3【Prison of Ego】: Weakness inflicted by【Shattered Flesh】is increased to 2 turns. At the start of battle, put a【Revel of the Void】into your hand.", "timestamp": "2026-01-01T12:09:47.787000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-10T16:29:44.669000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1456257856339709983", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Doorstain's dissoluted siste Rey-Khan OC kit (Meme sorta)", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_